thread.title_full: Your Biggest Fear (In One Word), Based On Your Zodiac Sign

author: Kris Miller
title: Your Biggest Fear (In One Word), Based On Your Zodiac Sign
text:
Kristopher Roller Aries (March 21st to April 19th) Boredom.
Taurus (April 20th to May 21st) Failure.
Gemini (May 22nd to June 21st) Decisions.
Cancer (June 22nd to July 22nd) Loneliness.
Leo (July 23rd to August 22nd) Solitude.
Virgo (August 23rd to September 22nd) Imperfection.
Libra (September 23rd to October 22nd) Instability.
Scorpio (October 23rd to November 22nd) Intimacy.
Sagittarius (November 23rd to December 21st) Predictability.
Capricorn (December 22nd to January 20th) Loss.
Aquarius (January 21st to February 18th) Expectations.
Pisces (February 19th to March 20th) Responsibility.
